{"title":"不愿同秋风絮语黄昏（外一首）","authors":["卢祖品"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":3,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿同秋风絮语黄昏（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卢祖品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我每天起来赶路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴冲冲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记不清跨过了几条河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记不清转过了几道弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记不清流了多少汗水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记不清爬了多少山岗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边采摘树种；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我停下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺手撒一把彩云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也象一粒种子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在广阔的世界飘荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我吹向远方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我每天早早儿赶路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是快乐地前行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使走上最后的途程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也惦记闻鸡起舞的岁月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿同秋风絮语黄昏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵树的愿望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人笑话我的姿势，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"模样儿也不好看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当然，我不会以大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来塑造自己的形象；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至不会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以大树来塑造自己的形象；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只是大森林中普普通通的一员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但为了长久激励着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"存在于心中的隐秘的愿望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了土地深情的期待，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了白云临别的赠言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也要长得象一座山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首在蓝天底下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象山一样雄伟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象山一样坚强。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}